item.title: The Best Royal Moments of 2023
item.description: Happy New Year, RoRos! And a very heartfelt thank you for your continuing support, we couldn’t do this without you and the wonderful community you’ve all built! We’re bringing you a special end-of-year episode full of YOUR favorite moments, plus Ladies Rachel and Roberta share their own “Crowns” and “Frowns” of 2023. From the Coronation of King Charles III (!!!) to SO. MANY. TIARAS., this year is going to be hard to top. Grab a glass of champagne, and take a stroll down memory lane with us... Feed: https://rss.art19.com/royally-obsessed
